Titolo: Futurama (video game)

Anno: 2003

Descrizione: Futurama is a 3D platform video game based on the science fiction animated series of the same name. Versions are available for the PlayStation 2 and Xbox, both of which use cel-shading technology. A GameCube port was planned for release, but it was cancelled for unknown reasons. The cutscenes of the game are presented as an entire "lost episode" of Futurama on the DVD of The Beast with a Billion Backs.